OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FA business owner in Pontypridd says he
OL,7,Fcould have suffered around #150,000
OL,8,Fworth of damage in the aftermath of
OL,9,FStorm Bert.
OL,11,FA major incident was declared in the
OL,12,FRhondda Cynon Taf region of south
OL,13,FWales on Sunday, with between 200 and
OL,14,F300 properties in the area affected by
OL,15,Fflooding.
OL,17,FGareth Davies is the owner of Scorpion
OL,18,FAutomotive Solutions, where cars were
OL,19,Falmost completely submerged in water
OL,20,Fdue to Storm Bert flooding at the
OL,21,Fweekend.
