OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FGareth and his partner had checked
OL,7,FCCTV footage the morning of Sunday, 24
OL,8,FNovember, to find six inches of water
OL,9,Fhad entered the garage.
OL,11,FUpon arriving at the premises, the
OL,12,Fwater had already reached knee height.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, he said: "I was
OL,15,Ftrying to salvage as much as I could
OL,16,Fwhen I got here: the computers, the
OL,17,Fcustomers' vehicles."
