OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FGesturing to a vehicle, he said: "This
OL,7,Fvehicle was down on the floor, I had
OL,8,Fto try to pull that together up to
OL,9,Fknee height in water to try and save
OL,10,Fthat vehicle. By the time I left here
OL,11,Fit was waist height and I was fighting
OL,12,Fto get out of the unit up to the dry
OL,13,Fpatch."
