OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FWhen asked about the cost to his
OL,7,Fbusiness, Gareth said: "You're
OL,8,Fprobably looking at close to #100,000
OL,9,Fworth of cars out there. With my
OL,10,Fcomputers and things in here, you're
OL,11,Flooking at #20,000-30,000 worth of
OL,12,Fdamage, plus the clean-up operation
OL,13,Fand the cost of all of that.
OL,15,F"We could be looking at #150,000 in
OL,16,Ftotal if I was to write all those cars
OL,17,Foff and replace everything that needs
OL,18,Freplacing in here all at once."
