OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FHe has been running his business from
OL,7,Fthe premises on Berw Road for around
OL,8,F18 months. Operating in a "flood risk"
OL,9,Farea, he says insurance will not
OL,10,F"cover a penny" of the damages which
OL,11,Fflooding has caused at the weekend.
OL,13,F"With insurance down here, being a
OL,14,Fflood-risk, any insurance wouldn't
OL,15,Fcover anything damaged by floods, and
OL,16,Feverything has been damaged by the
OL,17,Ffloods. So, the insurance doesn't
OL,18,Fcover a penny of it."
