OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FThe business owner said customers had
OL,7,Fbeen understanding but he may not feel
OL,8,Fthe knock-on effects for some time.
OL,10,F"A lot of customers have been quite
OL,11,Fgood about things, they understand
OL,12,Fthey may have come in for just a
OL,13,Ftiming belt but now it's going to be
OL,14,Fthree, four, five weeks before I even
OL,15,Fget to the point of knowing what's
OL,16,Fwrong with it and whether or not its
OL,17,Fviable to repair it," he said.
