OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,F"If it was your car and it has
OL,7,Fhappened to you once, you're going to
OL,8,Ftake it to another garage next time,
OL,9,Fand then I will have lost the business
OL,10,Fthat way. I'm not going to know what
OL,11,Fthe knock on effect of that is for a
OL,12,Ffew months yet."
OL,14,FAdding to his distress is the
OL,15,Fcomplication of spilled oil mixing
OL,16,Fwith the flood water.
