OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FHe explained: "The water was one
OL,7,Fthing, but obviously being a garage,
OL,8,Fyou have waste oil in here in
OL,9,Fcontainers. With the water coming up
OL,10,Fso high, it pushed the containers
OL,11,Fover, so you have about 200 to 250
OL,12,Flitres of oil mixing in with that
OL,13,Fwater. It has gone everywhere."
OL,15,FDue to the oil spill, the clean-up
OL,16,Foperation will not be a
OL,17,Fstraightforward task, and Gareth has
OL,18,Fhad to seek specialist advice on his
OL,19,Fnext steps.
