OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,F"A charity has come down here, they're
OL,7,Ftrying to help out now with
OL,8,Fenvironmental health and how we would
OL,9,Fgo about doing it," he said.
OL,11,F"It isn't a case of just taking
OL,12,Feverything out and jet washing it all
OL,13,Fdown, because all that water has to go
OL,14,Fsomewhere and it'll end up going down
OL,15,Fthe drain."
OL,17,FLike others in the area, Gareth
OL,18,Fbelieves residents and business owners
OL,19,Fshould have received more warning from
OL,20,Fofficials regarding the severity of
OL,21,Fthe storm.
