OL,3,CCar garage owner devastated by Storm
OL,4,CBert as flood bill could reach #150k
OL,6,FHe said: "There was a yellow warning,
OL,7,Fwhich I would naturally assume isn't
OL,8,Fgoing to cause this much damage. If
OL,9,Fit's a foot of water, it's one thing
OL,10,Fcleaning that up, but to the extent it
OL,11,Fwas... I wasn't expecting it, and I
OL,12,Fdon't think the other businesses on
OL,13,Fthe estate were expecting it."
OL,15,FRhondda Cynon Taf Council leader
OL,16,FAndrew Morgan has said the weather was
OL,17,Fworse than forecast and he was
OL,18,F"amazed" only a yellow weather warning
OL,19,Fhad been issued by the Met Office.
