OL,6,FThe Met Office has said a full
OL,7,Fassessment of the forecast and warning
OL,8,Fstrategy will take place over the
OL,9,Fcoming days, as with any named storm.
OL,11,FNatural Resources Wales is also set to
OL,12,Freview the warnings issued to
OL,13,Fresidents in Wales about the severity
OL,14,Fof Storm Bert.
